cs.CG, cs.DS, cs.GT, cs.SG, cs.NA. 

The paper deals with algorithms for reconstructing submanifolds, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG). The algorithm uses the witness complex, which is a tool from algebraic topology and computational topology (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the stability of power protection, which is a concept from computational geometry and topology (cs.GT). The algorithm does not rely on explicit coordinates of the points, but only on the distance matrix, which is a topic in metric geometry and numerical analysis (cs.SG, cs.NA).
